## 4. Optional: the Copilot DV agent pack

This environment was generated without the team's GitHub Copilot agent pack
(none was found next to uvm-gen, or it was disabled). To add it later, re-run
the generator with `--copilot-pack <path-to-pack-root>` — existing files are
never touched; the pack collateral (`.github/`, `docs/`, `dv/`,
`cockpit.ini`) is simply added. The agent workflow guide then lives in
`.github/USERGUIDE.md`, and `/start-here` in Copilot chat gives new
engineers a guided first session.
{% endif %}
